{"id": "1489437042596380903", "channel_id": "1435487123250872371", "type": 0, "author_id": "926398065231921174", "author_name": "universe.dark", "author_bot": false, "content": "4小強可以先練還有要玩的界融珠先換啟靈", "timestamp": "2026-04-03T01:31:03.357000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1489450156918177853", "channel_id": "1435487123250872371", "type": 0, "author_id": "920561286578856007", "author_name": "be_queitplease", "author_bot": false, "content": "单纯看你这个box现有角色的话\n血希和24都缺队友\n血希缺羊妈\n超维24缺3启温，深海24缺融朵\n\n不过这配置血希应该还能救\n你可以组血希，爱继丝，哈姆林，蕾娅/拉蒙娜", "timestamp": "2026-04-03T02:23:10.055000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1489451404937531482", "channel_id": "1435487123250872371", "type": 0, "author_id": "920561286578856007", "author_name": "be_queitplease", "author_bot": false, "content": "然后4合1池，反正你缺一大堆角色，可以适当地补一补角色\n\n你可以抽的是泰旖丝（2启），奥尔拉（1/3启），塔薇（超限），［弥利亚姆（2启），墨菲（1启），哈姆林（2启）］\n只要任意一个角色抽到推荐启灵后就直接停手不要再抽了", "timestamp": "2026-04-03T02:28:07.606000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-03T02:29:14.662000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
